Mechanism

Purpose

Pilot federations & UNPA

Proof-of-concept within and beyond current systems

Financial & tech incentives

Tangible benefits for early adopters

Participatory drafting

Legitimacy, inclusivity, and co-ownership

Early adopter prestige

Soft power and non-coercive alignment

Layered ratification

Democratic entry, even in resistant political climates

Citizen juries

